"{\"uid\": \"thepeninsulaqatar.com-article-23-06-2024-qnb-visa-credit-cardholders-win-all-inclusive-premium-travel-packages-to-olympic-games-paris-2024-courtesy-of-visa\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"News  Opinion  Writers  Videos  Editorials  Handbook  News  Opinion  Writers  Videos  Editorials  Handbook        Doha, Qatar:\\u00a0\\u00a0QNB, the leading financial institution in the Middle East and Africa, marked the successful conclusion of its Olympic Games campaign in collaboration with Visa.Six lucky QNB Visa credit cardholders have won all-inclusive premium travel packages for two to attend the Olympic Games Paris 2024, courtesy of Visa.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.999999993606707, \"rank\": 6.393343774596201e-09, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}, {\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6967575445263468e-15, \"text\": \"Visa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6967575445263468e-15, \"text\": \"Visa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each package comes with business class return tickets, premium hotel stay, tickets for the Olympics Games Paris 2024 and other gifts.During the two-month campaign, which ran from April to June 2024, QNB Visa credit cardholders automatically qualified for the draw upon meeting the required spend criteria.The campaign, designed to reward customer loyalty with unparalleled experiences, has seen a resounding success, generating significant engagement and enthusiasm among customers.One of the six lucky winners won a package for the opening ceremony, and another won a package for the closing ceremony.It is worthy to note that QNB is the only bank in Qatar to offer the opening and closing ceremony packages to the winners.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6967575445263468e-15, \"text\": \"Visa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7519429894070966e-17, \"text\": \"QNB\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.0320721329902988e-12, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"QNB remains committed to launching relevant campaigns and superior product features and benefits in addition to providing safe, convenient, and rewarding payment experiences to our customers.The Senior Executive Vice President of QNB Retail Banking Group, Adel Ali Al Malki said: \\\"We are extremely pleased with the overwhelming response and enthusiasm demonstrated by our cardholders.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7519429894070966e-17, \"text\": \"QNB\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7519429894070966e-17, \"text\": \"QNB\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/QNB_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\", \"score\": 0.9961894513648737, \"rank\": 0.0038251244577605197, \"text\": \"Adel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VIII\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 0.8848897077170784, \"rank\": 0.13008408940615096, \"text\": \"Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are thrilled to offer these unique opportunities, aligned with our continuous efforts to enhance customer engagement and experience.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We extend our gratitude to Visa, our long-term strategic partner, for this collaboration.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6967575445263468e-15, \"text\": \"Visa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our customers can look forward to even more rewarding campaigns in the near future.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1858, \"enti